  "texts": [
    "After completing the first phase, the participants were then thanked and invited to start the second phase.",
    "In the second phase of the study, participants were informed that each of the twenty stimulus texts were generated either by a human or an AI.",
    "They reviewed each text and its associated contextual information one by one in a randomized order.",
    "They were asked to identify the authorship of the stimulus text (see Figure 3).",
    "Prior to responding to the 20 stimuli, participants went through two training trials."
